# Cloud News Aggregator with Sentiment Analysis

## Description
This project pulls news articles using NewsAPI and analyzes their sentiment using PySpark and TensorFlow. Results are stored on Firebase.

## Setup
1. Install requirements: `pip install -r requirements.txt`
2. Run: `python cloud_main.py`

## Tools
- PySpark
- TensorFlow
- Firebase
- Kubernetes (for deployment)

## Note
Replace API keys with your own in the script.
